data.description: Beautiful Mid-Century Modern Cabin - Welcome to Your Own Personal Retreat In Forest Falls! Located just 15 minutes from Yucaipa & 20 minutes from Redlands, this Cabin offers the beauty of mountain living with easy access to the city. Living room w/ two fireplaces, skylight, and access to rear deck. Kitchen w/ dine-in bar. Spacious Master Bedroom w/ upgraded bathroom. Large rear deck w/ treetop views - perfect for entertaining! Basement/workshop area. Laundry room. Plenty of parking. Just minutes to the best hiking trails & Big Falls Waterfall. A unique opportunity that is not to be missed!
